<h2> What is AgileVentures?  </h2>
<p>
  AgileVentures is a non-profit organization and a community of people dedicated to crowdsourced learning and open source project development.  We are 
  fans of agile development, Test driven development and Pair Programming.  We develop in distributed teams, using tools for remote and online programming.
</p>

<p>
  The goal of AgileVentures is to allow anyone to be able to find a project, a team and a partner to work together and improve 
  their skills of software development, programming and project management.
</p>
<br />
