<h2> What exactly can I get out of participating  in AV?  </h2>

<em> Learn and gain experience </em>
<ol>
  <li>Participate in a real project, collaborate in a real team and work with real customers </li>
  <li>Learn to program, manage a project and manage a team </li>
  <li>Learn the industry tools for software development and project management </li>
  <li>Get immediate help and guidance on technical issues </li>
  <li>Get feedback on your work and ideas </li>
</ol>

<em> Realize yourself </em>
<ol>
  <li>Set up and run your own project </li>
  <li>Implement your ideas with the help of others </li>
  <li>Get recognition from the community </li>
  <li>Improve your leadership and management skills </li>
</ol>

<em> As a bonus </em>
<ol>
  <li>Get hired </li>
  <li>Just have fun, meet new people from all over the world and socialize </li>
</ol>

